Aww, still no comments?

Haha, in my rush to upload this, I failed to realize that I included a single 'messed up' file that is a full song and a first third of the next song. So, deal with it.

Ok, at the end of 'Kill with Style' from the album 'These past 5 years' there is a hidden track. The song should be about 4 min long but its 9. I have googled the lyrics about 20 times to no avail. Anyone have a clue what the hidden track is? It is a BRILLIANT acoustic track.
